                  --_--_--_--_--_--_--_--_--_--_--_--
                        Pollutant Propagation
                  --_--_--_--_--_--_--_--_--_--_--_--

Use:
  'make' to compile.
  'make clean' to remove the objects.
  './pollutant_propagation <input_file> <tolerance> <iterations>' to execute.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Input parameter necessary:
  'i)'   input_file.
  'ii)'  tolerance of convergence.
  'iii)' max number of iterations.

  Example: ./pollutant_propagation island/island.txt 0.0001 100
